SWIRL SEARCH 1.5

Cleaned up relevancy, finalized release notes, added install support, updated banners and versions
Removed install from swirl.py and moved it to install.py
Added install and tail options to swirl.py
Added length normalization, match_any operator, fixed issues in mixer, added nltk
Updated swirl support address, set explain=False as default
Finished Relevancy Modes, Fixed date_published, Added date_sort on relevancy tie
Large model for spacy, tweaked relevancy
Fixed status after rescore, set rescore timer to 3 seconds, run mixers even after post_result_processing error

SWIRL SEARCH 1.4

Documentation updates, moved Sqlite3 and PostGres init code into base class DBConnector, Explain set to True

SWIRL SEARCH 1.4

PostGresql connector, revised funding example for Sqlite and PostGres, improved relevancy, SWIRL_EXPLAIN in settings.py, 'core' (django and celery-worker) now an argument to swirl.py start/stop/restart, tags on all objects, default added to search providers

Documentation updates for Docker
